Q: HOW DOES THE COMPRESSION ZIPPER WORK? A: These organizers use a double-zipper system. First, zip the bag closed like a normal packing cube. Then, use the second compression zipper to flatten the bag, removing excess air and reducing thicknessby up to 50% to save space. Q: IS IT VACUUM COMPRESSION? A: No, These compression cubes feature double zippers to compress clothes by up to 40%~50%(Just zip to compress, no vacuum or pump), allowing you to pack more clothes in the suitcase . Q: ARE THESE BAGS MACHINE WASHABLE? A: We recommend hand washing these nylon packing cubes with mild soap and air drying to maintain the integrity of the compression zippers and water-resistant coating.
